---
title: Walnut-Crusted Salmon with Bacon and Squash Salad
description: Set the table and get ready to impress with this succulent salmon dish. It’s fancy enough for a special occasion and easy enough for a weeknight dinner. The crust is so delicious that you’ll be eating the loose bits straight off the tray. You can thank us later!
